name: Unidentified_Black_Sun_member_1
content: A Falleen individual was a member of the Black Sun criminal syndicate during the reign of the Galactic Empire. Between 3 ABY and 4 ABY, the Falleen visited Ord Mantell City on the planet Ord Mantell with another Falleen. After a gorgmonger attempted to sell a gorg to the bounty hunter T'onga, the pair confronted the gorgmonger about operating in the city despite the fact they had not paid protection fees. The gorgmonger countered that business was slow, and so they could not pay the fees, but the Falleen informed the gorgmonger that it was not Black Sun's problem. The other Falleen took one of the gorgs and ate it, and informed their colleague that they should try a gorg. The pair were then approached by members of the Unbroken Clan, who declared that Ord Mantell now belonged to them. In response, the two Falleen drew their blasters but were quickly killed by the Unbroken Clan individuals.
